>","new_url":"","id":"1054","checkdouble":"190732"},{"date":"07:22 09/07","title":"Tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111ang s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch 1966","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/tuyen-anh-dang-san-sang-lap-lai-chien-tich-1966.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, HLV Gareth Southgate chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh.\r\n</h2><h2>Tam S\u01b0 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1eeba qua, \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c v\u00e0 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0. C\u00e1c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Harry Maguire c\u00f9ng Dele Alli \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Tam S\u01b0 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a h\u00e8 Italia n\u0103m 1990.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 mu\u1ed1n \u0111i xa h\u01a1n th\u1ebf. H\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c v\u00e0 \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng, l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch n\u0103m 1966. Cho \u0111\u1ebfn nay, \u0111\u00f3 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, HLV Gareth Southgate cho bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tri \u00e2n l\u1edbn h\u01a1n th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 1966. \u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n v\u00ec sao \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u0103m \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng k\u1ef3 World Cup tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Gareth Southgate chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e1n k\u1ebft h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Gareth Southgate chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e1n k\u1ebft h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/HLV-Gareth-Southgate-chia-se-ve-co-hoi-cua-DT-Anh-truoc-ban-ket-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gareth Southgate chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 1966, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0o n\u0103m \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1ch h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh danh. N\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch n\u00e0y, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 s\u1ebd c\u00f2n \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3 h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u00f4i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0110T B\u1ec9.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i cho nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch trong d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n. Hi\u1ec7n nay, ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u0111ang b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5, v\u00e0 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u00f2n l\u1edbn h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Gareth Southgate chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi \u0110T Croatia, Tam S\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o h\u1ecd s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi trang ph\u1ee5c \u00e1o tr\u1eafng qu\u1ea7n tr\u1eafng, d\u00f9 v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. Croatia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 &lsquo;\u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0&rsquo;, nh\u01b0ng b\u1ed9 s\u1ecdc ca-ro \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1eafng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u00f9ng m\u00e0u v\u1edbi Tam S\u01b0, b\u1edfi v\u1eady Modric v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1eb7c \u00e1o xanh \u0111en.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-vao-ban-ket-sau-3-thap-ky-fan-cuong-nhay-tu-xe-bus-xuong-an-mung-421-190684.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/anh-vao-ban-ket-sau-3-thap-ky-fan-cuong-nhay-tu-xe-bus-xuong-an-mung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-vao-ban-ket-sau-3-thap-ky-fan-cuong-nhay-tu-xe-bus-xuong-an-mung-421-190684.html\">Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft sau 3 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7, fan cu\u1ed3ng&hellip; nh\u1ea3y t\u1eeb xe bus xu\u1ed1ng \u0103n m\u1eebng</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a fan h\u00e2m m\u1ed9, v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ngu d\u1ed1t c\u0169ng v\u1eady. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V tuy\u1ec3n Anh nh\u1ea3y t\u1eeb xe bus 2 t\u1ea7ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0103n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Tam...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/dt-anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-2018-khi-xu-angle-phu-bong-len-lich-su-466-190667.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/dt-anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-2018-khi-xu-angle-phu-bong-len-lich-su.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/dt-anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-2018-khi-xu-angle-phu-bong-len-lich-su-466-190667.html\">\u0110T Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: Khi x\u1ee9 \u0102ng-l\u00ea ph\u1ee7 b\u00f3ng l\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed</span><br>\r\nMang b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 - \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u1ea9u hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay \u0111ang ph\u1ee7...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/ban-ket-world-cup-2018-man-utd-dung-thu-hai-ve-so-cau-thu-gop-mat-465-190664.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/ban-ket-world-cup-2018-man-utd-dung-thu-hai-ve-so-cau-thu-gop-mat.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/ban-ket-world-cup-2018-man-utd-dung-thu-hai-ve-so-cau-thu-gop-mat-465-190664.html\">B\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: Man Utd \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 hai v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh m\u00e0 n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 \u0111ang th\u1eafng l\u1edbn khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n 50 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 \u0111ang thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf c\u00e1c c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1053","checkdouble":"190733"},{"date":"07:55 09/07","title":"Kane mu\u1ed1n Tam S\u01b0 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/kane-muon-tam-su-la-doi-bong-cuoi-cung-tai-nuoc-nga.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa, ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga s\u1ebd kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00f9ng \u0110T Anh.\r\n</h2><h2>Tam S\u01b0 mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh c\u00fap v\u00e0ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00e1c, nh\u01b0ng \u0110T Anh \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh 1 trong 4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, qua \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft sau g\u1ea7n 3 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 v\u00e0 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane \u0111ang \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau r\u1ea5t cao cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Anh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch n\u0103m 1966, l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 duy nh\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1nh l\u1edbn, Kane \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y Sir Geoff Hurst, ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1eadp hattrick trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 1966 l\u00e0m ni\u1ec1m c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 l\u00e2u r\u1ed3i k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi \u0110T Anh l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn. Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 1966, v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t tinh th\u1ea7n&rdquo; &ndash; ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Tottenham cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Harry Kane \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00f9ng \u0110T Anh\" title=\"Harry Kane \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/kane-muon-tam-su-la-doi-bong-cuoi-cung-tai-nuoc-nga.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Kane \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00f9ng \u0110T Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5, tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m \u1edf trong l\u1eabn ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n c\u1ecf \u0111\u1ec3 truy\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, \u0111em l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m vui cho nh\u1eefng C\u0110V theo d\u00f5i \u0110T Anh, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, b\u1edfi t\u00f4i c\u0169ng t\u1eebng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb l\u1edbn l\u00ean v\u1edbi m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110T. V\u00ec v\u1eady, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y l\u00fac n\u00e0y, d\u1eabn d\u1eaft to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o. Kh\u00f4ng ai mu\u1ed1n v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 s\u1edbm, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p&rdquo; &ndash; Harry Kane \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00f9ng \u0110T Anh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay, Kane \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi. Anh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1 hy v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tuyen-anh-dang-san-sang-lap-lai-chien-tich-1966-421-190733.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/tuyen-anh-dang-san-sang-lap-lai-chien-tich-1966.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tuyen-anh-dang-san-sang-lap-lai-chien-tich-1966-421-190733.html\">Tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111ang s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch 1966</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, HLV Gareth Southgate chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-vao-ban-ket-sau-3-thap-ky-fan-cuong-nhay-tu-xe-bus-xuong-an-mung-421-190684.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/anh-vao-ban-ket-sau-3-thap-ky-fan-cuong-nhay-tu-xe-bus-xuong-an-mung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-vao-ban-ket-sau-3-thap-ky-fan-cuong-nhay-tu-xe-bus-xuong-an-mung-421-190684.html\">Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft sau 3 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7, fan cu\u1ed3ng&hellip; nh\u1ea3y t\u1eeb xe bus xu\u1ed1ng \u0103n m\u1eebng</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a fan h\u00e2m m\u1ed9, v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ngu d\u1ed1t c\u0169ng v\u1eady. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V tuy\u1ec3n Anh nh\u1ea3y t\u1eeb xe bus 2 t\u1ea7ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0103n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Tam...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-anh-vs-thuy-dien-461-190635.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/214818-3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-anh-vs-thuy-dien-461-190635.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 0-2 Anh (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nC\u00e1c pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Harry Maguire v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Dele Alli \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1052","checkdouble":"190734"},{"date":"08:09 09/07","title":"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia l\u1ea5y Messi ra d\u1ecda tuy\u1ec3n Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/truoc-dai-chien-nguoi-croatia-lay-messi-ra-doa-tuyen-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Croatia chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Tam S\u01b0 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, v\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y HLV Dalic \u0111e d\u1ecda \u0110T Anh b\u1eb1ng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 b\u1eaft ch\u1ebft Harry Kane.\r\n</h2><h2>Croatia t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1nh l\u1edbn<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 t\u1edbi Moscow tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o s\u1ecdc ca-ro s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua d\u00e0n s\u01b0 t\u1eed tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a HLV Gareth Southgate. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, Croatia ph\u1ea3i ng\u0103n kh\u00f4ng cho \u0110T Anh ghi b\u00e0n, hay n\u00f3i c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 b\u1eaft ch\u1ebft c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y &ndash; ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 v\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u1ee9ng Leo Messi, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Croatia &ndash; Zlatko Dalic tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. \u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Kane v\u00e0 Sterling l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Dalic \u0111e d\u1ecda \u0110T Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1nh l\u1edbn\" title=\"HLV Dalic n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/hlv-croatia-len-tieng-thach-thuc-anh-o-ban-ket.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Dalic \u0111e d\u1ecda \u0110T Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1nh l\u1edbn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 \u0110T Anh, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tin v\u00e0o \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Harry Kane l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n anh \u1ea5y. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u1ee9ng Lionel Messi v\u00e0 Christian Eriksen, v\u00ec v\u1eady hy v\u1ecdng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169ng s\u1ebd ng\u0103n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Kane.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng \u0110T Anh kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu n\u00e0o d\u1ec5 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y. H\u1ecd \u0111ang \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. \u0110T Anh \u0111ang ch\u01a1i th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ef1c di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc trong nh\u1eefng pha d\u00e0n x\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t. Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 cao to c\u1ee7a Anh c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 nguy hi\u1ec3m trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Raheen Sterling l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi \u0110T Anh. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t nhanh v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi Harry Kane. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng Croatia s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng h\u1ecd.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tin v\u00e0o s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Dalic \u0111e d\u1ecda \u0110T Anh b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/luka-modric-phat-bieu-sau-tran-croatia-vs-nga-421-190676.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/luka-modric-phat-bieu-sau-tran-croatia-vs-nga.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/luka-modric-phat-bieu-sau-tran-croatia-vs-nga-421-190676.html\">Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 chuy\u1ec7n Croatia b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n Anh \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup</span><br>\r\nLuka Modric ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Nga. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 32 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Croatia c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c cho b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Anh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dalic-phat-bieu-sau-tran-croatia-vs-nga-421-190675.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/dalic-phat-bieu-sau-tran-croatia-vs-nga.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dalic-phat-bieu-sau-tran-croatia-vs-nga-421-190675.html\">HLV Croatia kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea7m n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Nga</span><br>\r\nZlatko Dalic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Nga. Thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Croatia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh may m\u1eafn h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m x\u00fac sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1051","checkdouble":"190735"},{"date":"08:33 09/07","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Paulinho \u0111i th\u1eadt xa \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1... Trung Qu\u1ed1c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/12/21/chinh-thuc-tien-ve-paulinho-roi-barca-chi-sau-11-thang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00eda Barcelona \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paulinho tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u H\u1eb1ng \u0110\u1ea1i ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, ch\u1ec9 11 th\u00e1ng sau quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i.\r\n</h2><h2>Paulinho ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c r\u1eddi Barca<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2017, G\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalonia \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c khi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Paulinho \u2013 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Trung Qu\u1ed1c, v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u euro. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn gi\u00fap Barca v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap gi\u1ea3i qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay Paulinho ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Brazil ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u H\u1eb1ng \u0110\u1ea1i. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a, anh \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i r\u1ed3i tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Trung Qu\u1ed1c ch\u1ec9 sau 11 th\u00e1ng phi\u00eau l\u01b0u t\u1ea1i La Liga.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Barca v\u00e0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Paulinho. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 30 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i CLB Trung Qu\u1ed1c theo m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t 50 tri\u1ec7u euro, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n 10 tri\u1ec7u euro so v\u1edbi l\u00fac Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 anh m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paulinho tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u sau 11 th\u00e1ng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Barca\" title=\"Paulinho tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u sau 11 th\u00e1ng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/pau.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Paulinho tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u sau 11 th\u00e1ng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paulinho Bezerra, v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn mua \u0111\u1ee9t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp theo cho CLB Trung Qu\u1ed1c\u201d \u2013 trang web ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Barca \u0111\u01b0a tin. \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 bi\u1ebft \u01a1n v\u1edbi Paulinho v\u1ec1 cam k\u1ebft, s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 ch\u00fac anh \u1ea5y may m\u1eafn, th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Paulinho tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u sau 11 th\u00e1ng gia nh\u1eadp Barca, \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ch\u01a1i t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 49 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ghi 9 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh 2 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch (La Liga v\u00e0 c\u00fap Nh\u00e0 vua). \u1ede c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 55 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110T Brazil v\u00e0 ghi 13 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Anh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1ea5t Selecao \u1edf k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/paulinho-thua-bi-con-dau-don-hon-tran-thua-duc-17-469-190586.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/paulinho-thua-bi-con-dau-don-hon-tran-thua-duc-17.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/paulinho-thua-bi-con-dau-don-hon-tran-thua-duc-17-469-190586.html\">Paulinho: Thua B\u1ec9 c\u00f2n \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn h\u01a1n tr\u1eadn thua \u0110\u1ee9c 1-7</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paulinho cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c Brazil b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf World Cup 2018 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn thua \u0110\u1ee9c 1-7 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/bong-da-va-cuoc-phieu-luu-kho-tin-cua-paulinho-389-190453.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/bong-da-va-cuoc-phieu-luu-kho-tin-cua-paulinho.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-vat/bong-da-va-cuoc-phieu-luu-kho-tin-cua-paulinho-389-190453.html\">B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c phi\u00eau l\u01b0u kh\u00f3 tin c\u1ee7a Paulinho</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1eddi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, m\u1ea5y ai \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec? V\u00e0 t\u00f4i, \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n t\u00e2m ni\u1ec7m r\u1eb1ng, Paulinho c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u Evergrande, \u1edf Trung Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 Paulinho \u1edf Barcelona c\u0169ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-bi-461-190551.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-bi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-bi-461-190551.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9 (T\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nSau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Uruguay tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9 l\u00e0 Brazil c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua B\u1ec9 1-2. M\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Tite tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh \u2013 TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1050","checkdouble":"190739"},{"date":"08:50 09/07","title":"Evra khuy\u00ean Ronaldo t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU, gia nh\u1eadp Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/evra-khuyen-ronaldo-tu-choi-mu-gia-nhap-juventus.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Patrice Evra tin r\u1eb1ng Juventus l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ec3 Ronaldo ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.</h2><h2>Ronaldo s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Real Madrid h\u00e8 n\u00e0y sau nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed5 v\u1ee1 quan h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi HLV Florentino Perez. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i gia c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia l\u00e0 Juventus \u0111ang l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u1eadt l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a CR7 v\u1ec1 Turin v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-dung-luong-sieu-khung-du-ronaldo-tro-lai-old-trafford-172-183045.html\" target=\"_blank\">Man United \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0a Ronaldo tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford</span>. <br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Evra khuy\u00ean Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Evra khuy\u00ean Ronaldo t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU, gia nh\u1eadp Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Evra khuy\u00ean Ronaldo t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU, gia nh\u1eadp Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/evra-khuyen-ronaldo-tu-choi-mu-gia-nhap-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Evra khuy\u00ean Ronaldo t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU, gia nh\u1eadp Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng Evra, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i cho c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng cho r\u1eb1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n Ronaldo n\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Italia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cM\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u h\u1ecfi t\u00f4i r\u1eb1ng Ronaldo n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn Juventus hay Man United. T\u00f4i th\u00ec v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Ronaldo v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 n\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi n\u0103m 2050, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p h\u01a1n th\u1ebf. \u0110\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u1eady th\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Juventus. B\u1edfi v\u00ec sau qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Man United, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1ea1y. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd \u0103n ch\u00e1o \u0111\u00e1 b\u00e1t n\u00ean Juve s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n \u1edf trong tr\u00e1i tim t\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Ronaldo r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn. C\u1eadu bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia y\u00eau c\u1eadu th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 hy sinh n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ebfn Juve. C\u1eadu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y m\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Juve, Ronaldo s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i \u1edf k\u1ef3 World Cup ti\u1ebfp theo ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t linh v\u1eadt c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ronaldo:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/modric-khong-tin-ronaldo-se-roi-real-180-190697.html\">Modric kh\u00f4ng tin Ronaldo s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/cuu-chu-tich-canh-bao-real-ve-y-dinh-ban-ronaldo-180-190689.html\">C\u1ef1u ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Real v\u1ec1 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1049","checkdouble":"190744"},{"date":"08:44 09/07","title":"Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i th\u00edch VAR b\u1eaft tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/9/trong-tai-thich-var-bat-tran-ban-ket-phap-vs-bi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay, Andres Cunha \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft 1 World Cup 2018, Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 1h \u0111\u00eam ng\u00e0y 11/7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Ph\u00e1p qu\u1ea3 c\u00f3 duy\u00ean v\u1edbi c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i mang qu\u1ed1c t\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia m\u00e0 h\u1ecd t\u1eebng lo\u1ea1i \u1edf World Cup 2018. N\u1ebfu \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Uruguay, l\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Argentina (\u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 thua Ph\u00e1p 3-4 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8), Nestor Pitana c\u1ea7m c\u00f2i, th\u00ec t\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft s\u1eafp t\u1edbi g\u1eb7p B\u1ec9, th\u1eadt tr\u00f9ng h\u1ee3p v\u00e0 th\u00fa v\u1ecb khi \u00f4ng vua \u00e1o \u0111en ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7m c\u00e2n n\u1ea3y m\u1ef1c.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u00f4ng tin, ch\u00e2n dung gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng tin, ch\u00e2n dung gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/trong-tai-ban-ket-phap-bi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Andres Cunha t\u1eebng b\u1eaft tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p th\u1eafng \u00dac 2-1 g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng xa l\u1ea1 v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i 41 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y, b\u1edfi \u00f4ng t\u1eebng b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a s\u1eafc \u00e1o Lam v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \"b\u1ebb c\u00f2i\" sau khi tham kh\u1ea3o VAR \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p th\u1eafng \u00dac 2-1 g\u00e2y n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng \u00edt tranh c\u00e3i sau \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed World Cup. \u00d4ng Andres Cunha ban \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh vi ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Risdon ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Griezmann \u1edf ph\u00fat ph\u00fat 54 tuy nhi\u00ean sau khi \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng VAR, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cho Ph\u00e1p h\u01b0\u1edfng 11m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Ph\u00e1p c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 kh\u00e1c (Goal-Line) \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Pogba. \u00d4ng Andres Cunha c\u00f2n c\u1ea7m c\u00f2i tr\u1eadn kh\u00e1c \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng: T\u00e2y Ban Nha th\u1eafng Iran 1-0 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"O tran Tay Ban Nha 1-0 Iran, trong tai Uruguay cung dung cong nghe VAR\" title=\"\u1ede tr\u1eadn T\u00e2y Ban Nha 1-0 Iran, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Uruguay c\u0169ng d\u00f9ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/trong-tai-ban-ket-phap-bi-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn T\u00e2y Ban Nha 1-0 Iran, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Uruguay c\u0169ng d\u00f9ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng trong hi\u1ec7p 2, Iran \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, nh\u01b0ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn sau khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i tham kh\u1ea3o VAR v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn ra m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u00e3 vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u00f3ng \u0111i v\u00e0o khung th\u00e0nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i Andres Cunha l\u00e0m nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu c\u1ea7m c\u00f2i \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i Copa America (gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia Nam M\u1ef9), Copa Libertadores (t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng UEFA\u00a0Champions League).</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1048","checkdouble":"190745"},{"date":"22:05 08/07","title":"S\u00f4i s\u1ee5c c\u00f9ng clip nh\u1ea1c ch\u1ebf c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng cho World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/soi-suc-cung-clip-nhac-che-co-dong-cho-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>World Cup 2018 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch hay nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. V\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean, 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga c\u0169ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n28 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00f4i v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. Nh\u1eefng \u00f4ng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ee9c, T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Argentina r\u1ed3i m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 Brazil \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eaft tay nhau v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1edbm h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh. D\u00f9 bu\u1ed3n, vui, h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng hay th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea3m x\u00fac kh\u00f4n t\u1ea3 m\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 mang \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 trong g\u1ea7n 1 th\u00e1ng qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa l\u00e0 World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i. C\u00f3 h\u01a1i ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u max h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, max k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00f2a chung trong s\u1ef1 s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn n\u00f3c c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn xin g\u1eedi t\u1edbi qu\u00fd \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3, kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ca kh\u00fac nh\u1ea1c ch\u1ebf &quot;Kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean b\u00f3ng&quot; d\u1ef1a theo b\u00e0i h\u00e1t &quot;Kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m x\u00fac&quot; nh\u01b0 l\u1eddi c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng thi\u1ebft th\u1ef1c cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. C\u1ea3m \u01a1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, c\u1ea3m \u01a1n World Cup 2018!<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/8/nhac-che-khong-quen-bong.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>L\u1eddi nh\u1ea1c v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n: Tika T\u00f9ng Anh</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\nBao nhi\u00eau l\u00e2u ta kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ed3i \u0111\u00e2y<br>\r\nBao nhi\u00eau l\u00e2u ch\u01b0a xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e2y<br>\r\nH\u00f4m nay anh em ta ng\u1ed3i \u0111\u00e2y<br>\r\nB\u00e0n l\u1ea1i chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a n\u0103m nay<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRonaldo n\u0103m nay ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng<br>\r\nC\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u00ecnh qu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng may kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao l\u00e2u<br>\r\nTh\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i anh ra v\u1ec1<br>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ebft th\u00fac, n\u0103m nay Si l\u1ea1i u\u1ea5t \u1ee9c<br>\r\nAnh ch\u01a1i trong s\u1ef1 c\u00f4 \u0111\u01a1n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi bao nhi\u00eau th\u00e1ng n\u0103m \u1edf b\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i anh<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 l\u1ebd Anh n\u0103m nay l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng<br>\r\nTuy qu\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u si\u00eau sao<br>\r\nTh\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng Anh v\u1eabn ch\u01a1i v\u1eabn v\u00f4 v\u00f2ng trong<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadt qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem b\u00f3ng<br>\r\nM\u1ed7i t\u1ed1i r\u00ecnh r\u00ecnh<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn s\u00e1ng th\u00ecnh l\u00ecnh<br>\r\nAnh em c\u00f9ng nhau&nbsp; ta th\u00e2u \u0111\u00eam<br>\r\nD\u1eabu bi\u1ebft s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t m\u1ec7t<br>\r\nMai anh em \u0111i l\u00e0m r\u1ed3i<br>\r\nV\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n ng\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i<br>\r\nB\u00ean ly r\u01b0\u1ee3u n\u00e0y<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu b\u1eaft ta ng\u1eebng xem b\u00f3ng<br>\r\nS\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c <br>\r\nS\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m g\u00ec <br>\r\nTh\u00f4i ta n\u1edd \u0111i ta xem ti\u1ebfp<br>\r\nC\u1ed1 th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e1ng v\u1eady<br>\r\nAnh em ta tuy m\u1ec7t r\u1ed3i<br>\r\nV\u1eabn c\u1ed5 ng\u1ea9ng \u0111\u1ea7u<br>\r\nXem b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i d\u00e0i<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBao nhi\u00eau l\u00e2u ta kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ed3i \u0111\u00e2y<br>\r\nBao nhi\u00eau l\u00e2u ch\u01b0a xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e2y<br>\r\nH\u00f4m nay anh em ta ng\u1ed3i \u0111\u00e2y<br>\r\nB\u00e0n l\u1ea1i chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a n\u0103m nay<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u0103m nay anh em tin n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c<br>\r\nV\u1eady m\u00e0 gi\u1edd h\u1ecd v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc lu\u00f4n<br>\r\nUruguay kh\u00f4ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua France<br>\r\nH\u1ecd nh\u1eadn thua ra v\u1ec1<br>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ebft th\u00fac, T\u00e2y ban nha ph\u1ea3i thua Nga<br>\r\nN\u0103m nay kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00ean \u0111\u00e2u<br>\r\nTh\u1ebf n\u00ean th\u00f4i 4 n\u0103m ti\u1ebfp theo l\u1ea1i ch\u01a1i<br>\r\nTi\u1ebfp n\u1eefa, Neymar \u0103n v\u1ea1 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111em l\u1ea1i Win \u0111\u00e2u<br>\r\nTh\u1ebf n\u00ean th\u00f4i ch\u00fang ta c\u1ee9 \u0111i v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadt qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem b\u00f3ng<br>\r\nM\u1ed7i t\u1ed1i r\u00ecnh r\u00ecnh<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn s\u00e1ng th\u00ecnh l\u00ecnh<br>\r\nAnh em c\u00f9ng nhau&nbsp; ta th\u00e2u \u0111\u00eam<br>\r\nGi\u1eabu bi\u1ebft s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t m\u1ec7t<br>\r\nMai anh em \u0111i l\u00e0m r\u1ed3i<br>\r\nV\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n ng\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i<br>\r\nB\u00ean ly r\u01b0\u1ee3u n\u00e0y<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu b\u1eaft ta ng\u1eebng xem b\u00f3ng<br>\r\nS\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c <br>\r\nS\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m g\u00ec <br>\r\nTh\u00f4i ta n\u1edd \u0111i ta xem ti\u1ebfp<br>\r\nC\u1ed1 th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e1ng v\u1eady<br>\r\nAnh em ta tuy m\u1ec7t r\u1ed3i<br>\r\nV\u1eabn c\u1ed5 ng\u1ea9ng \u0111\u1ea7u<br>\r\nXem b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i d\u00e0i<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Bongda24h.vn (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1047","checkdouble":"190716"},{"date":"22:12 08/07","title":"HLV Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ch\u00ea ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn, HLV V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh.\r\n</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, HLV V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch Sanna Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ch\u00ea ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ch\u00ea ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/cong-phng_kv8pj4j0zvgm1iag592kifipy.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a cho r\u1eb1ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ed1 \u00fd ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng n\u00f3i: \"T\u00f4i ngh\u0129, t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng vi\u1ec7c n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh, nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean y t\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00e2u gi\u1edd, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n va ch\u1ea1m ng\u00e3 b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. T\u00f4i \u0111\u1ee9ng xa qu\u00e1, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 nh\u01b0ng h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1edbi v\u00e0 n\u00e9m b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i t\u00f4i b\u00eanh v\u1ef1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u0169 c\u1ee7a HAGL l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Duy Thanh \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u00e0 t\u00ednh c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t, chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 h\u1ecd c\u00f2n t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi HAGL nh\u01b0ng h\u00f4m nay h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t th\u00eam v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, \u00f4ng T\u00e2n cho bi\u1ebft th\u00eam: \"H\u00f4m nay, HAGL ham t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn cho h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 h\u1edf nhi\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng ph\u00eda sau nhi\u1ec1u h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u0111\u00e3 khai th\u00e1c kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Theo t\u00f4i, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i r\u1ea5t l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t v\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn b\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng l\u00e0 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat kinh nghi\u1ec7m t\u1eeb c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc, khi c\u00f3 b\u00e0n thua s\u1edbm \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng dao \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ecb thua th\u00eam, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc. Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a h\u00f4m nay r\u1ea5t t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Pleiku, Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 tr\u00ean BXH v\u1edbi 31 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 18 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u. \u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf nh\u00f3m cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 Bi\u1ec3n s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i th\u00eam m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong-168-190714.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong-168-190714.html\">HLV HAGL l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng thi\u1ebfu fair-play c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh cho r\u1eb1ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/hagl-vs-khanh-hoa-vong-18-vleague-2018-372-190694.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hagl-vs-khanh-hoa-vong-18-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/hagl-vs-khanh-hoa-vong-18-vleague-2018-372-190694.html\">HAGL 2-4 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a (KT): Th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 t\u1ec7, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai thua s\u1ea5p m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp HAGL vs Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u HAGL vs Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a v\u00f2ng 18 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1046","checkdouble":"190717"},{"date":"22:31 08/07","title":"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m x\u00fac. Trong \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t v\u1eabn l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm 6-3 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 18 V-League.</h2><h2>1. H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i b\u0103ng b\u0103ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">'Con t\u00e0u' H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p tr\u1edf ng\u1ea1i tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch V-League 2018. Ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 TP.HCM tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby \u1edf v\u00f2ng 18 V-League 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng quy\u1ebfn r\u0169 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ee9c \u00e9p c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0, CLB TP.HCM ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng trong kho\u1ea3ng 25 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi sau c\u00fa ra ch\u00e2n hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft sau m\u1ed9t pha ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p trung l\u1ed9 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e2m l\u00fd v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i th\u0103ng hoa h\u01a1n trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 6-3 \u0111\u1eadm nh\u1ea5t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng gi\u00fap th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u1edbi 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sau v\u00f2ng 18 V-League M\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u0103ng hoa c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sau v\u00f2ng 18 V-League M\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u0103ng hoa c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/DMH_3858(1).jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh tr\u01b0\u1edbc TP.HCM t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 18 V-League</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\u00a0</p>\r\n<h2>2. M\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf v\u00f2ng 18 V-League\u00a0</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">29 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi trong 7 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 18. \u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed gi\u1ea3i V-league. V\u1edbi 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi, tr\u1eadn H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 6-3 TP.HCM l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3 nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 8/7, Qu\u1ea3ng Nam v\u00e0 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a h\u00f2a nhau trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng chia \u0111\u1ec1u cho hai \u0111\u1ed9i. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng song h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ec3 cho \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c, Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm 5-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1. M\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u c\u0169ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa HAGL vs Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a. 'G\u1ed7' v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm song sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u00eam th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 2-4 kh\u00e1 cay \u0111\u1eafng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Pleiku.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V-League r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t x\u00fac t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 h\u01a1n, qua \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1o s\u1ee9c h\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00e9o kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian l\u00e3ng qu\u00ean V-League \u0111\u1ec3 '\u0103n ng\u1ee7' c\u00f9ng World Cup.</p>\r\n<h2>3. \u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Oseni \u0111ang 't\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i' trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 th\u00ec c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea1i \u0111ang t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 thu h\u1eb9p kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi ngo\u1ea1i binh H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u00f2ng 18 V-League ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 t\u1edbi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh c\u1ee7a B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng. V\u1edbi c\u00fa hat-trick b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o sinh n\u0103m 1997 \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t s\u00e1t th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tien dao Tien Linh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ti\u1ebfn Linh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/3/nguyen-tien-linh-xuat-sac-nhat-vleague-thang-5.png\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ti\u1ebfn Linh \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao t\u1ea1i V-League 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u0169ng gi\u00fap Ti\u1ebfn Linh thu h\u1eb9p kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi Oseni xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 4 b\u00e0n. N\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, Ti\u1ebfn Linh \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ee9ng sau Ti\u1ebfn Linh v\u1edbi \u0111\u00fang 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u00edt h\u01a1n l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a SLNA. S\u1ef1 th\u0103ng hoa c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 v\u1edbi m\u1ea1ch 6 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp trong th\u1eddi gian qua. Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c chi\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 quan.</p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/8/Highlight-Quang-Nam-vs-Binh-Duong.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<h2>4. C\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng nh\u00f3m cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3 4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng l\u00e0 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 CLB TP.HCM c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u1edf v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y, cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng v\u1eabn \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 v\u1edbi 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng TP.HCM v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t tuy nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh (gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m) c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 TP.HCM v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t. N\u0103m nay V-League s\u1ebd c\u00f3 1,5 su\u1ea5t xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng. Do \u0111\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9a \u0111\u1ea7y nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH V-League sau vong 18\" title=\"BXH V-League sau v\u00f2ng 18\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/BXH-V-League-sau-vong-18.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>BXH V-League sau v\u00f2ng 18</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-kich-tinh-hagl-24-khanh-hoa-168-190725.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-kich-tinh-hagl-24-khanh-hoa.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-kich-tinh-hagl-24-khanh-hoa-168-190725.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh HAGL 2-4 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 s\u1edbm song CLB HAGL cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a. V\u00e0...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi-168-190720.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/14/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi-168-190720.html\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb ch\u00ea, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao-168-190717.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao-168-190717.html\">HLV Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ch\u00ea ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn, HLV V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau-168-190719.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau-168-190719.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u</span><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, Nguy\u1ec5n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o h\u00e0nh vi ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p HAGL.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1045","checkdouble":"190719"},{"date":"23:02 08/07","title":"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb ch\u00ea, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/14/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o v\u1edbi 'ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh' Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/14/hagl-len-tieng-truoc-tin-don-chieu-mo-thu-mon-dt-lao.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh cho r\u1eb1ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa hai CLB HAGL vs Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 8/7, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng to ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh v\u00ec cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n c\u00e2u gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1edd tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebft th\u00fac.\u00a0Tuy nhi\u00ean n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh \u0111\u00e3 'minh oan' cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\u00a0</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng T\u1ea5n Anh cho bi\u1ebft: \"Ngay sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u1ecfi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ea5y th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n c\u00f3 \u00fd tr\u00ec ho\u00e3n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, n\u00ean ch\u1ea1y l\u1ea1i n\u00f3i: '\u0110\u1ee9ng d\u1eady \u0111i, c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u00e2u m\u00e0 n\u1eb1m'. M\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a th\u1ea5y v\u1eady li\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea9y Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ra, nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn x\u1ea5n l\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n n\u00ean b\u1ecb th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL c\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh n\u00ean k\u00ecm ch\u1ebf, tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 x\u1ea3y ra trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng khi cho r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00ean ph\u00eda Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a c\u00f3 l\u1eddi l\u1ebd x\u00fac ph\u1ea1m, khi\u00eau kh\u00edch khi\u1ebfn Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi n\u1ed5i n\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3n \u1eefng d\u1eef d\u1ed9i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau-168-190719.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau-168-190719.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u</span><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, Nguy\u1ec5n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o h\u00e0nh vi ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p HAGL.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao-168-190717.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao-168-190717.html\">HLV Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ch\u00ea ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn, HLV V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong-168-190714.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong-168-190714.html\">HLV HAGL l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng thi\u1ebfu fair-play c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh cho r\u1eb1ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1044","checkdouble":"190720"},{"date":"00:11 09/07","title":"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh HAGL 2-4 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-kich-tinh-hagl-24-khanh-hoa.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 s\u1edbm song CLB HAGL cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh n\u00e0y.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<h2>1. H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 HAGL v\u1eabn thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 nh\u01b0 ng\u00e0y n\u00e0o</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a CLB HAGL t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i t\u1edbi m\u1ee9c n\u00e0o. L\u00fac n\u00e0y h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong 4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i khi \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1edbi 32 l\u1ea7n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng v\u00e0 hai CLB \u1edf nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf l\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 TP.HCM.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n Ti\u1ebfn ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ea3n b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 ch\u1ec9 \u1edf m\u1ee9c trung b\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n nh\u1eefng c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn HAGL 2-4 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn HAGL 2-4 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/Diem-nhan-tran-HAGL-2-4-Khanh-Hoa-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn HAGL 2-4 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a l\u00e0 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a G\u1ed7\u00a0</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u00e1ch V\u0103n Ti\u1ebfn, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd 'G\u1ed7' l\u00ean nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 \u0110\u00f4ng Tri\u1ec1u v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay anh \u1edf hi\u1ec7p 2 l\u00e0 A S\u00e2n. Sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00f4ng Tri\u1ec1u v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch c\u00f3 li\u1ec1n 2 b\u00e0n t\u1eeb ph\u00fat 39 \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 44 do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a ngo\u1ea1i binh Youssouf Toure.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, e r\u1eb1ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 CLB HAGL c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch trong t\u1ed1p 5 nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1 ra tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</p>\r\n<h2>2. D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u00e2n binh</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ed9i HAGL thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t, 'G\u1ed7' \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 an \u1ee7i khi hai t\u00e2n binh m\u00e0 h\u1ecd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n th\u1ee9 hai cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia Josip Zeba \u0111\u00e3 ghi d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n v\u1edbi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb pha treo b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, ngo\u1ea1i binh m\u1edbi n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. \u0110\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2, Josip ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Osmar t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-2, song t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap HAGL gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u1edfi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabu sao vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c ngo\u1ea1i binh HAGL ghi b\u00e0n trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai, khi m\u00e0 h\u1ecd v\u1ed1n v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng ngo\u1ea1i binh gi\u1ecfi trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.</p>\r\n<h2>3. M\u00e0n t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eeba tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau m\u1ed9t l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t v\u00ec \u0103n \u0111\u1ee7 3 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng, th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i h\u00f4m nay (8/7) g\u1eb7p Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y bu\u1ed3n cho ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ngh\u1ec7 An khi anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng do l\u1ed7i ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng \u1edf cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cong Phuong\" title=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t y\u00eau c\u1ea7u khi b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. Trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u1edf ph\u00fat 22, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat g\u1ed1c Ngh\u1ec7 An d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea1m nhanh nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ea9y ra. T\u1edbi ph\u00fat 28, anh l\u1ea1i x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba v\u00e0 c\u1ee9a l\u00f2ng v\u1ecdt x\u00e0 trong t\u01b0 th\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb ai theo k\u00e8m.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00ecn chung, \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c nh\u01b0ng anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra c\u00e1ch g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 xuy\u00ean ph\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ed1t c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u01b0 Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh. Trong ph\u00fat n\u00f3ng n\u1ea3y, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng v\u00ec h\u00f9ng h\u1ed5 g\u00e2y h\u1ea5n v\u1edbi Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh, khi cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n c\u00e2u gi\u1edd. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ngh\u1ec7 An v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng ch\u00fang.</p>\r\n<h2>4. Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a cho th\u1ea5y b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL, CLB Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn nh\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu l\u00e9p v\u1ebf.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ecd phong t\u1ecfa g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 k\u00edn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0o khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh r\u1ed3i m\u01b0\u1ee3n s\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Toure c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 tinh qu\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ed1c Ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ec3 tung ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t l\u00ean b\u00f3ng s\u1eafc l\u1ea1nh.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu may m\u1eafn h\u01a1n, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 bi\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t set qu\u1ea7n v\u1ee3t tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Tr\u00f9m T\u1ec9nh d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m d\u1ed9i x\u00e0 ngang ph\u00fat 84 v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0o thay anh l\u00e0 Ho\u00e0i An s\u00fat b\u00f3ng ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ed9t trong th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n Ti\u1ebfn.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn HAGL 2-4 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn HAGL 2-4 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/36787800_1815071101918501_4864050149187387392_n.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>5. Th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n t\u1ea1i Pleiku gi\u00fap Sanna Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i FLC Thanh H\u00f3a. L\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n \u0111ang c\u00f3 31 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 t\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 hai tr\u00ean BXH.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 19, xem ra kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 Bi\u1ec3n l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c nh\u1ecf, tuy nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu gi\u1eef v\u1eefng phong \u0111\u1ed9 h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 hai chung cu\u1ed9c.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, HAGL c\u1ea7n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u01a1n n\u1eefa sau tr\u1eadn thua v\u1eeba qua. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c tr\u1eafng tay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, HAGL \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb SLNA v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean BXH. L\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 24 \u0111i\u1ec3m, k\u00e9m 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m so v\u1edbi SLNA v\u00e0 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi t\u1ed1p 3. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng 8 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u sinh t\u1eed c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH V-League sau vong 18\" title=\"BXH V-League sau v\u00f2ng 18\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/BXH-V-League-sau-vong-18.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>BXH V-League sau v\u00f2ng 18</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi-168-190720.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/14/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi-168-190720.html\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb ch\u00ea, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau-168-190719.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau-168-190719.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u</span><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, Nguy\u1ec5n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o h\u00e0nh vi ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p HAGL.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao-168-190717.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao-168-190717.html\">HLV Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ch\u00ea ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn, HLV V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong-168-190714.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong-168-190714.html\">HLV HAGL l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng thi\u1ebfu fair-play c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh cho r\u1eb1ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1043","checkdouble":"190725"},{"date":"01:02 09/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n v\u00f2ng 18 V-League: M\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u0103ng hoa c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/diem-nhan-vong-18-vleague-mua-ban-thang-va-su-thang-hoa-cua-ha-noi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m x\u00fac. Trong \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t v\u1eabn l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm 6-3 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 18 V-League.</h2><h2>1. H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i b\u0103ng b\u0103ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">'Con t\u00e0u' H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p tr\u1edf ng\u1ea1i tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch V-League 2018. Ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 TP.HCM tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby \u1edf v\u00f2ng 18 V-League 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng quy\u1ebfn r\u0169 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ee9c \u00e9p c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0, CLB TP.HCM ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng trong kho\u1ea3ng 25 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi sau c\u00fa ra ch\u00e2n hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft sau m\u1ed9t pha ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p trung l\u1ed9 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e2m l\u00fd v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i th\u0103ng hoa h\u01a1n trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 6-3 \u0111\u1eadm nh\u1ea5t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng gi\u00fap th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u1edbi 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sau v\u00f2ng 18 V-League M\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u0103ng hoa c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sau v\u00f2ng 18 V-League M\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u0103ng hoa c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/DMH_3858(1).jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh tr\u01b0\u1edbc TP.HCM t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 18 V-League</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\u00a0</p>\r\n<h2>2. M\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf v\u00f2ng 18 V-League\u00a0</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">29 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi trong 7 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 18. \u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed gi\u1ea3i V-league. V\u1edbi 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi, tr\u1eadn H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 6-3 TP.HCM l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3 nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 8/7, Qu\u1ea3ng Nam v\u00e0 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a h\u00f2a nhau trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng chia \u0111\u1ec1u cho hai \u0111\u1ed9i. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng song h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ec3 cho \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c, Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm 5-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1. M\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u c\u0169ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa HAGL vs Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a. 'G\u1ed7' v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm song sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u00eam th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 2-4 kh\u00e1 cay \u0111\u1eafng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Pleiku.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V-League r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t x\u00fac t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 h\u01a1n, qua \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1o s\u1ee9c h\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00e9o kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian l\u00e3ng qu\u00ean V-League \u0111\u1ec3 '\u0103n ng\u1ee7' c\u00f9ng World Cup.</p>\r\n<h2>3. \u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Oseni \u0111ang 't\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i' trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 th\u00ec c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea1i \u0111ang t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 thu h\u1eb9p kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi ngo\u1ea1i binh H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u00f2ng 18 V-League ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 t\u1edbi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh c\u1ee7a B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng. V\u1edbi c\u00fa hat-trick b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o sinh n\u0103m 1997 \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t s\u00e1t th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tien dao Tien Linh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ti\u1ebfn Linh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/3/nguyen-tien-linh-xuat-sac-nhat-vleague-thang-5.png\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ti\u1ebfn Linh \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao t\u1ea1i V-League 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u0169ng gi\u00fap Ti\u1ebfn Linh thu h\u1eb9p kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi Oseni xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 4 b\u00e0n. N\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, Ti\u1ebfn Linh \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ee9ng sau Ti\u1ebfn Linh v\u1edbi \u0111\u00fang 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u00edt h\u01a1n l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a SLNA. S\u1ef1 th\u0103ng hoa c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 v\u1edbi m\u1ea1ch 6 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp trong th\u1eddi gian qua. Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c chi\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 quan.</p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/8/Highlight-Quang-Nam-vs-Binh-Duong.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<h2>4. C\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng nh\u00f3m cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3 4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng l\u00e0 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 CLB TP.HCM c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u1edf v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y, cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng v\u1eabn \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 v\u1edbi 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng TP.HCM v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t tuy nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh (gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m) c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 TP.HCM v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t. N\u0103m nay V-League s\u1ebd c\u00f3 1,5 su\u1ea5t xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng. Do \u0111\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9a \u0111\u1ea7y nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH V-League sau vong 18\" title=\"BXH V-League sau v\u00f2ng 18\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/BXH-V-League-sau-vong-18.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>BXH V-League sau v\u00f2ng 18</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-kich-tinh-hagl-24-khanh-hoa-168-190725.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-kich-tinh-hagl-24-khanh-hoa.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-kich-tinh-hagl-24-khanh-hoa-168-190725.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh HAGL 2-4 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 s\u1edbm song CLB HAGL cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a. V\u00e0...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi-168-190720.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/14/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi-168-190720.html\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb ch\u00ea, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao-168-190717.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-khanh-hoa-che-tien-dao-cong-phuong-da-lao-168-190717.html\">HLV Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ch\u00ea ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn, HLV V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau-168-190719.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau-168-190719.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u</span><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, Nguy\u1ec5n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o h\u00e0nh vi ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p HAGL.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1042","checkdouble":"190726"},{"date":"01:14 09/07","title":"Th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm CLB TP.HCM, HLV H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u1eabn khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/thang-dam-clb-tphcm-hlv-ha-noi-van-khiem-ton-noi-ve-co-hoi-vo-dich.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng 70, 80% c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch khi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm CLB TPHCM, HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm CLB TPHCM, HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/3/Thang-dam-CLB-TPHCM,-HLV-Chu-Dinh-Nghiem-noi-ve-co-hoi-vo-dich-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng 70, 80% c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u mu\u1ed9n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u00f2ng 18 V-League, CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch TP.HCM v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eadm 6-3. Th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i n\u00e0y gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 duy tr\u00ec kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi nh\u00f3m b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i.\u00a0</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam 3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u1eefa, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch s\u1edbm V-League 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng khi chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. \u00d4ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn: \u201cN\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i th\u00ec t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng 70, 80%\".\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i trong m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y, HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam cho r\u1eb1ng, \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng n\u00e0y l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb khi l\u00e0m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb th\u00eam v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB TP.HCM, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn: \"Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 phung ph\u00ed r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. Vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn l\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn CLB nh\u01b0ng vi\u1ec7c m\u1ea5t \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng khi\u1ebfn CLB m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t m\u1eaft x\u00edch trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh. V\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p qu\u00e1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 th\u1eeba s\u1ee9c gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/diem-nhan-vong-18-vleague-mua-ban-thang-va-su-thang-hoa-cua-ha-noi-168-190726.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/diem-nhan-vong-18-vleague-mua-ban-thang-va-su-thang-hoa-cua-ha-noi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/diem-nhan-vong-18-vleague-mua-ban-thang-va-su-thang-hoa-cua-ha-noi-168-190726.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n v\u00f2ng 18 V-League: M\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u0103ng hoa c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i</span><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m x\u00fac. Trong \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t v\u1eabn l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm 6-3 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/ha-noi-vs-tphcm-vong-18-vleague-2018-372-190695.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/ha-noi-vs-tphcm-vong-18-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/ha-noi-vs-tphcm-vong-18-vleague-2018-372-190695.html\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 6-3 TPHCM (KT): Ho\u00e0ng V\u0169 Samson l\u1eadp poker trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n nh\u1ea5t V-League 2018</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs TPHCM: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh v\u00f2ng 18 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1041","checkdouble":"190727"}]}